About this item

  • 4K UltraHD Resolution - Experience incredible detail with 4X the resolution of 1080p Full HDTVs.
  • High Brightness LED Backlight - Enjoy a brilliant picture in any room.
  • Enhanced Color - Enhanced color bringing rich, vibrant images to life.
  • Motion Rate 240 with MEMC Frame Insertion - Combines multiple motion enhancement technologies for best-in-class motion clarity.
  • Fire TV Experience All your entertainment in one place. Fire TV gives you quick access to live TV, video games, music, and lets you stream over 1 million movies and TV episodes. Subscriptions may apply.
  • HDR PRO+ with Dolby Vision, HDR10+, HDR10, & HLG - Enjoy enhanced contrast, accurate colors and fine details utilizing all the most advanced HDR formats.
  • Auto Game Mode (ALLM) - Automatically enables game mode for the lowest possible input lag and latency for an unmatched gaming performance.
  • Dolby Atmos Audio - Advanced spatial audio processing found in movies, TV shows, and video games.
  • Enhanced Dialogue Mode - Audio Setting for better clarity and intelligibility in movies, TV shows, and video games.
  • DTS Virtual:X - Advanced audio post-processing for your everyday content offering an immersive 3D sound, all from just your TV speakers.

    Product Description

    TCL S5 Class Smart TVs offer stunning 4K HDR picture quality with four times the resolution of Full HD for enhanced clarity and detail, all wrapped together in an elegant edge-to-edge FullView 360 metal bezel-less design blending seamlessly into any home. The new High Brightness LED backlight produces a brilliant image in any home. HDR PRO+ delivers bright and accurate colors for a lifelike viewing experience with support for Dolby Vision, HDR10+, HDR10, and HLG. In addition, with Motion Rate 240 with MEMC frame insertion, your favorite shows, movies, and sporting events are enhanced for exceptional motion clarity. Game Accelerator 120* VRR provides fast, fluid gameplay without lag. Additionally, Dolby Atmos and DTS Virtual:X are supported, enhancing your audio experience, and enabling virtualized 3D sound using only your TV speakers. An all-new Enhanced Dialogue mode provides better audio clarity for your TV Shows, movies, and video games. TCL S Class TVs are more than just a Smart TV, but a Smart Choice.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Great value for the money
    UPDATE 12/10/24: While everything I wrote still stands, I have discovered you CAN NOT disable the SLEEP TIMER.! This is a HUGE DESIGN FLAW and IMMENSELY AGGRAVATING & INCONVENIENT! Example: Every time I pause a show (to answer phone etc), the TV goes into Sleep Mode and I have to Start the process All Over again; Go to & click Hulu (any app), click my name, scroll to show I was watching, Click on show, then Click "play". Unbelievable waste of time and IRRITATING to No End! While researching how to disable the sleep timer, I found so many forums with many, manh people discusing this issue and how P!ssed off everyone is about this horrible issue. Why they don't have "Never" option in the sleep timer is the most idiotic oversight. If I had discovered this within my return window, I would have got rid of this TV. Unless they fix this in the future, I will NEVER EVER buy another Fire TV! ROKU is so much more user-friendly and not trying to force things on the user (like Amazon TV). Are there work arounds? Yes there are but they are only temporary and jusr another step you have to redo offten.The Color is fantastic and the picture is pretty great as far as backlight, brightness, and sharpness. It seemed smaller than my last TCL 55" but I measured it and it was the same size. I'm still trying to get used to the Home page layout of the Fire OS - I prefer Roku. 3 things that bothered me about this T.V.: 1.) I'm disappointed that the 3.5 mm headphone jack will not output to my multimedia speakers (with subwoofer), like my last TCL. I did all the proper settings and no sound at all. Luckily, the onboard TV speaker sound is better than most TV's if you tweak the settings a bit. It's good enough that I didn't feel compelled to buy a sound bar immediately (may get one eventually).2.) Like other reviews mentioned, there is a lag sometimes. It's just enough to be annoying but nothing to pull your hair out over...so far. I will update if anything gets worse with time.3) This is my worst pet peeve about this TV - I hate the remote! It's too long, overly sensitive (easy to trigger), and not very efficient with the button layout imo. But I have small hands so maybe that's why. Having Alexa makes up for some of my dislikes.All in all, this is an excellent TV for the price and a great deal. I like that it has a Media Player (app) so I can see stuff from a thumb drive right on my T.V. Lets see how long it lasts. The T.V. that I was replacing, a 55" TCL 5 series with Roku, the video went out 4 months after the 4 year extended warranty expired. Good thing I didn't pay for the extended warranty lol.

    • Stephen
      5.0 out of 5 stars A Compelling Blend of Size, Smart Features, and Affordability
      Reviewed in the United States on February 18, 2025
      Size: 75 inchesStyle: TV onlyVerified Purchase
      There are televisions, and then there are immersive entertainment experiences. The TCL 75-Inch Class S5 UHD 4K LED Smart TV (75S551F, 2024 Model) is not just a screenit is a window into a world of breathtaking color, cinematic sound, and seamless smart integration.
      Picture Quality That Stands Out

      Clarity, contrast, and colorthese are the hallmarks of a great TV. The 4K Ultra HD resolution on this display renders every detail with razor-sharp precision, while the Dolby Vision, HDR10+, HDR10, and HLG formats elevate contrast and color accuracy for a picture that feels alive. Whether you're watching a blockbuster movie or the big game, the TCL S5 Series ensures a premium visual experience.
      A Smart TV That Thinks Ahead

      Why waste time scrolling when you can speak your commands into existence? With Fire TV built-in, you have instant access to Netflix, Prime Video, Disney+, and thousands of other streaming options. But what truly sets this model apart is Alexa integrationjust say the word, and your TV obeys. No clunky remotes, no endless scrolling.
      Designed for Gamers, Built for Action

      In the world of gaming, every millisecond counts. Thats why the Game Accelerator 120 feature delivers 120Hz Variable Refresh Rate (VRR) for buttery-smooth motion. Add in Auto Game Mode (ALLM) and you have a TV that reacts as fast as you do, eliminating lag and maximizing performance.
      Audio That Commands Attention

      A great picture is only half the story. Dolby Atmos and DTS Virtual:X create an immersive soundstage that brings explosions, dialogue, and soundtracks to life. For true home theater enthusiasts, a soundbar may still be a wise addition, but the built-in speakers hold their own better than most in this category.
      What You Need to Know

      Lets be clearat this price, you are not getting OLED. Viewing angles could be wider, and for those who crave deeper blacks, the lack of local dimming may leave something to be desired. But in its class, the S5 delivers exceptional valuecompeting with TVs twice its price and leaving budget competitors in the dust.
      The Final Word: A Must-Have for Value Seekers

      If youre looking for a massive, high-performance 4K TV with smart features, fast gaming response, and brilliant visualsthis is the one to buy. The TCL 75-Inch S5 UHD 4K LED Smart TV is a powerhouse of entertainment, designed to impress without breaking the bank.
